text:
Katie Finucane is an Australian water polo player and coach. She competed for the Australian women's national water polo team in the 2007 Holiday Cup and 2007 FINA Women's Water Polo World League.
She graduated from Curtin University. She played for the Fremantle Marlins. She coached for the Fremantle Marlins.
